In order, the series goes #327738 (1-2), #244453 (3), #340855 (4-5), #322905 (7-11), then this one; #342710 (13). For those curious about what 6 and 12 are: Volume 6 is the compilation of volumes 1-5, and Volume 12 is the compilation of volumes 7-11. Other than the newest one, there are no untranslated parts to the story.

As @sambucety said, the two stories are by different people from the same circle. The reason you haven't seen stories like it included with previous chapters is that the other releases were translated from compilation volumes of just Futaba's Story.

This volume is a newer release that only contained one chapter about Futaba, so the circle included another futa story by a different member of the group to beef it up.

And seeing as more futa is always a good idea, I figured it'd be best to have it translated, too!
